The,MasterCard,Fraud,Scoring,for,Merchants,API,is,a,risk,management,solution,for,card,payments,The,API,facilitates,the,calculation,of,risk,probabilities,associated,with,payment,authorizations,for,card,transactions,It,uses,a,risk,scoring,range,of,between,and,to,show,the,likelihood,of,fraud,on,outside,payment,authorizations,with,higher,scores,signaling,higher,fraud,occurrence,probabilities,Developers,can,schedule,the,API,to,process,requests,at,the,beginning,of,the,authorization,process,or,at,the,user,s,preferred,time